Package: rhmc
Type: Package
Title: Hamiltonian Monte Carlo in R
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Victhor S. Sartório
Maintainer: Victhor S. Sartório <victhor@dme.ufrj.br>
Description: Implements simple Hamiltonian Monte Carlo routines in R for
             sampling from any desired target distribution which is continuous
             and smooth. Automatic parameter selection is not supported.
